00:04:35.500 --> 00:04:37.042 align:middle line:10%
you brought up the
adrenals, it seems

00:04:37.042 --> 00:04:41.080 align:middle line:10%
like everyone I interview, all
paths, especially clinicians,

00:04:41.080 --> 00:04:44.980 align:middle line:10%
