back to the adrenals.

00:04:44.980 --> 00:04:46.120 align:middle line:90%
Why is that?

00:04:46.120 --> 00:04:49.690 align:middle line:84%
>>THOMPSON: Well, they're
our intermediaries.

00:04:49.690 --> 00:04:54.040 align:middle line:84%
