your external environment

00:04:54.040 --> 00:04:55.480 align:middle line:90%
and your internal environment.

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:59.140 align:middle line:84%
And they and the
brain work together

00:04:59.140 --> 00:05:04.186 align:middle line:84%
in helping us live in this
world, whatever that might be.

00:05:04.186 --> 00:05:10.420 align:middle line:84%
Might be dealing with a
sick house syndrome, mold,

00:05:10.420 --> 00:05:12.520 align:middle line:84%
something somebody
just said to you.

00:05:12.520 --> 00:05:15.580 align:middle line:84%
Maybe somebody is quickly
running down the hall right now

00:05:15.580 --> 00:05:16.750 align:middle line:90%
and I jump.

00:05:16.750 --> 00:05:19.010 align:middle line:10%
How do I-- how do
I react to that?

00:05:19.010 --> 00:05:21.950 align:middle line:84%
My adrenal glands, my
brain are working together

00:05:21.950 --> 00:05:27.920 align:middle line:84%
to help me create a balancing
act with it all or not.

00:05:27.920 --> 00:05:32.270 align:middle line:84%
And all of that leads to this
incredible hormonal cascade,

00:05:32.270 --> 00:05:36.390 align:middle line:84%
which then tips off all the
different hormones in the body,

00:05:36.390 --> 00:05:39.150 align:middle line:84%
not the least of which
is the sex hormones.

00:05:39.150 --> 00:05:41.510 align:middle line:84%
But those adrenal glands
play such a huge role

00:05:41.510 --> 00:05:44.372 align:middle line:84%
in how pretty much
everything else happens.

00:05:44.372 --> 00:05:45.830 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: And so,
we're essentially

00:05:45.830 --> 00:05:48.680 align:middle line:10%
on adrenal overload
as a society,

00:05:48.680 --> 00:05:51.440 align:middle line:10%
or adrenal depletion,
whatever you want to call it.

00:05:51.440 --> 00:05:55.220 align:middle line:10%
I mean both, I suppose, because
we're choosing to live a life.

00:05:55.220 --> 00:05:58.610 align:middle line:10%
I mean, just the mere fact that
we're in the information age

00:05:58.610 --> 00:06:01.220 align:middle line:10%
really has changed the way
in which our adrenals have

00:06:01.220 --> 00:06:02.330 align:middle line:10%
to function.

00:06:02.330 --> 00:06:04.060 align:middle line:10%
I've forgotten the--

00:06:04.060 --> 00:06:06.560 align:middle line:10%
I've forgotten the
statistics exactly,

00:06:06.560 --> 00:06:08.870 align:middle line:10%
but it's something
like our minds

00:06:08.870 --> 00:06:12.560 align:middle line:10%
