00:06:15.532 --> 00:06:17.240 align:middle line:10%
through all the forms
of media that we're

00:06:17.240 --> 00:06:20.090 align:middle line:10%
surrounded with on a
day in, day out basis.

00:06:20.090 --> 00:06:21.427 align:middle line:90%
>>THOMPSON: Yeah.

00:06:21.427 --> 00:06:22.760 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That's a lot of input.

00:06:22.760 --> 00:06:23.950 align:middle line:90%
We weren't designed for that.

00:06:23.950 --> 00:06:25.408 align:middle line:84%
>>THOMPSON: Well,
we weren't, but I

00:06:25.408 --> 00:06:29.070 align:middle line:84%
think we're designing ourselves
for that, in that direction.

00:06:29.070 --> 00:06:30.380 align:middle line:90%
We have to.

00:06:30.380 --> 00:06:32.480 align:middle line:84%
I mean, that's the
great thing about man.

00:06:32.480 --> 00:06:33.980 align:middle line:90%
We can change.

00:06:33.980 --> 00:06:36.260 align:middle line:90%
And we can create newness.

00:06:36.260 --> 00:06:39.480 align:middle line:84%
But we have to
have strong organs.

00:06:39.480 --> 00:06:41.960 align:middle line:84%
And we have to-- and in
regards to the adrenals,

00:06:41.960 --> 00:06:45.350 align:middle line:84%
we have to really protect
them, and support them, and not

00:06:45.350 --> 00:06:48.140 align:middle line:84%
disregard them,
and cast them aside

00:06:48.140 --> 00:06:51.860 align:middle line:84%
with alcohol, with
caffeine, with white sugar,

00:06:51.860 --> 00:06:54.890 align:middle line:84%
and with chemicals, and
all the processed foods.

00:06:54.890 --> 00:06:56.660 align:middle line:90%
We can't do that stuff.

00:06:56.660 --> 00:06:59.900 align:middle line:84%
I mean, yeah, a
party here or there.

00:06:59.900 --> 00:07:01.880 align:middle line:84%
We can't carry on
like that every day.

00:07:01.880 --> 00:07:05.750 align:middle line:84%
We have to really honor
the fact that these glands,

00:07:05.750 --> 00:07:08.780 align:middle line:84%
and the brain, need
nutrients, and need

00:07:08.780 --> 00:07:10.970 align:middle line:84%
to be able to
function well in order

00:07:10.970 --> 00:07:14.090 align:middle line:84%
to do what you want
to do, which is

00:07:14.090 --> 00:07:16.170 align:middle line:90%
to lead a passion, joyful life.

00:07:16.170 --> 00:07:16.970 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

