00:07:20.870 --> 00:07:23.730 align:middle line:10%
I mean, it's not uncommon
to talk about your liver,

00:07:23.730 --> 00:07:25.850 align:middle line:10%
for example, or your kidneys.

00:07:25.850 --> 00:07:27.350 align:middle line:10%
In this culture,
