00:29:49.920 --> 00:29:51.128 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That's interesting.

00:29:51.128 --> 00:29:53.610 align:middle line:10%
Now, going back
to that link again

00:29:53.610 --> 00:29:56.700 align:middle line:10%
in the disruption of the
