things don't actually get
out of the body when--

00:30:23.430 --> 00:30:24.930 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: As a
result of using them.

00:30:24.930 --> 00:30:26.138 align:middle line:90%
Talk about that a little bit.

00:30:26.138 --> 00:30:27.290 align:middle line:90%
What gets left behind?

00:30:27.290 --> 00:30:29.810 align:middle line:84%
We think we're-- a lot of
people are really addicted

00:30:29.810 --> 00:30:33.350 align:middle line:84%
to cleansing and stuff and
really throwing a lot of stuff

00:30:33.350 --> 00:30:35.090 align:middle line:90%
at that.

00:30:35.090 --> 00:30:38.060 align:middle line:84%
What's the downside of
that aggressive kind

00:30:38.060 --> 00:30:39.740 align:middle line:84%
of cleansing from
the outside rather

00:30:39.740 --> 00:30:40.960 align:middle line:90%
than inside biologically?

00:30:40.960 --> 00:30:42.460 align:middle line:84%
>>THOMPSON: Well,
OK, I guess I just

00:30:42.460 --> 00:30:45.500 align:middle line:84%
want to make a distinction
between laxatives

00:30:45.500 --> 00:30:46.370 align:middle line:90%
and cleansing.

00:30:46.370 --> 00:30:47.510 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah, I'm
kind of throwing

00:30:47.510 --> 00:30:48.680 align:middle line:90%
the two in the same basket.

00:30:48.680 --> 00:30:52.070 align:middle line:84%
Let's just talk laxatives and
not your annual cleansing,

00:30:52.070 --> 00:30:54.610 align:middle line:84%
your spring
housecleaning, as it were.

00:30:54.610 --> 00:30:58.730 align:middle line:84%
>>THOMPSON: Well, the laxatives
are just artificially softening

00:30:58.730 --> 00:31:00.680 align:middle line:90%
the stool, pretty much.

00:31:00.680 --> 00:31:07.200 align:middle line:84%
