of residues that are left in--

00:31:07.200 --> 00:31:08.840 align:middle line:84%
you can talk to
colon therapists,

00:31:08.840 --> 00:31:11.720 align:middle line:90%
and they can tell you--

00:31:11.720 --> 00:31:14.840 align:middle line:84%
residues that are left
lining the intestines, which

00:31:14.840 --> 00:31:18.407 align:middle line:84%
