00:33:05.090 --> 00:33:07.160 align:middle line:10%
in terms of the kinds of
chemicals they create?

00:33:07.160 --> 00:33:09.230 align:middle line:84%
And explain what
chemicals they do create

00:33:09.230 --> 00:33:11.150 align:middle line:90%
and how they affect us.

00:33:11.150 --> 00:33:14.510 align:middle line:84%
>>THOMPSON: Well, I mean,
fun and pleasure, of course.

