>>REGINA: I'm just asking you
from a chemical point of view,

00:33:17.670 --> 00:33:18.470 align:middle line:90%
you know?

00:33:18.470 --> 00:33:21.590 align:middle line:84%
>>THOMPSON: Well, I think it
depends on what is causing--

00:33:21.590 --> 00:33:24.380 align:middle line:84%
you know, I mean,
is it really fun?

00:33:24.380 --> 00:33:25.220 align:middle line:90%
I tell you, I did--

00:33:25.220 --> 00:33:26.553 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: That's why I'm asking.

