are lower than that of males.

00:36:33.360 --> 00:36:35.235 align:middle line:10%
And I don't know if you
found the same thing.

00:36:35.235 --> 00:36:36.235 align:middle line:10%
>>THOMPSON: That's true.

00:36:36.235 --> 00:36:38.040 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: And that
also, the balance

00:36:38.040 --> 00:36:40.770 align:middle line:10%
of the alpha state
within our brains

00:36:40.770 --> 00:36:43.883 align:middle line:10%
is something that is also
lower than with males.

00:36:43.883 --> 00:36:46.050 align:middle line:10%
So this seems to be this
thing you're talking about,

00:36:46.050 --> 00:36:51.360 align:middle line:10%
this kind of mild depression,
having your emotions stressed

00:36:51.360 --> 00:36:54.810 align:middle line:10%
more easily than a men,
for example, is very real

00:36:54.810 --> 00:36:56.400 align:middle line:10%
on a chemical level.

