00:37:10.370 --> 00:37:11.170 align:middle line:90%
I don't know.

00:37:11.170 --> 00:37:12.600 align:middle line:90%
That might not even be right.

00:37:12.600 --> 00:37:14.700 align:middle line:84%
That might just be
a woman saying that.

00:37:14.700 --> 00:37:15.850 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right, exactly.

00:37:15.850 --> 00:37:19.410 align:middle line:10%
That's why I was just
keeping it to brain chemicals

00:37:19.410 --> 00:37:21.550 align:middle line:10%
and talking about
the alpha state.

00:37:21.550 --> 00:37:22.350 align:middle line:90%
>>THOMPSON: Yeah.

00:37:22.350 --> 00:37:25.980 align:middle line:84%
So I think that women have
to pay particular attention

00:37:25.980 --> 00:37:35.550 align:middle line:84%
to really getting spiritually or
emotionally, mentally balanced

00:37:35.550 --> 00:37:38.292 align:middle line:90%
and keeping their guts strong.

00:37:38.292 --> 00:37:39.750 align:middle line:84%
Really, really
important, because I

00:37:39.750 --> 00:37:43.230 align:middle line:84%
think women are
also more sort of

00:37:43.230 --> 00:37:48.600 align:middle line:84%
attracted to the craving foods
and the coffee, the chocolate

00:37:48.600 --> 00:37:50.670 align:middle line:90%
at 4:00 PM, that type of thing.

00:37:50.670 --> 00:37:52.890 align:middle line:90%
And that's not going to do it.

00:37:52.890 --> 00:37:54.200 align:middle line:90%
That's just the Band-Aid.

00:37:54.200 --> 00:37:55.000 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:37:55.000 --> 00:37:55.800 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:37:55.800 --> 00:37:57.300 align:middle line:84%
Now, you brought
this up earlier,

00:37:57.300 --> 00:37:58.630 align:middle line:90%
and it's time to talk about it.

00:37:58.630 --> 00:38:01.580 align:middle line:84%
So if a person is thinking,
oh, I'm kind of like that.

00:38:01.580 --> 00:38:03.650 align:middle line:90%
I'm not happy a lot of the time.

00:38:03.650 --> 00:38:05.400 align:middle line:84%
I just-- I don't know
